name: Cutting Teeth and Other Stories - By Erik Gamlem
description: This is a collection of five stories, including a trilogy of sorts, about the small moments and big moments in life. Love and loss and loneliness are abound in these five thrilling tales. I'm pretty into these suckers and I am psyched that this is done. Lovers of Raymond Carver or Jamcia Kincaid will probably dig this. Also people that drink, smoke and sip coffee at odd hours of the day. Get into it.

name: Death Language - Poems By Erik Gamlem
description: I used to write a bunch of poems and stuff. I put out a chap book in 2003 called Death Language. It's pretty cool. I really like the cover. It's like 53 pages. Poems are about death, drinking, alienation, old friends, good friends and women with guitars. There are some cute pictures of me as well.

name: With Sunlight Interfering - Poems and Essays By Katy Otto
description: Back in 2003 I took my first bonus from my SUPER FUN corporate job and published a book by my dear friend Katy Otto. It's 92 pages of poems and a collection of essay's Katy wrote during her time with Bald Rapunzel. It's totally inspiring and I am totally proud of it and totally stoked to have an easy way of offering it to the public. You should get this now, immediately.

name: KYS Super Fun Pack - Six Issues!
description: Catch up on all the issues of Korrupt Yr Self. The supper fun pack currently has issues 1-6 available. Read an interview with Turboslut. Explore the life on the road with Ghost Mice. Get all the details from Mike Law of New Idea Society. Learn about Skin Cancer and totally read amazing other stuff in Issue #5 and #6! The super fun pack is awesome and only four are available. This is the only way to get issue #2, which is a really good issue.

name: Current Issue of Korrupt Yr Self!
description: That's right, get the current issue of Korrupt Yr Self Zine Sent to your house from me. Currently we are on issue #6 where I talk about my experiences in New Mexico to date. It's pretty awesome.
